        "subject": "Oferta especial — 10% OFF no Pix",
        "text": "",
        "html": "<html><body style=\"font-family:sans-serif;background:#0f0f0f;color:#e8e8e8;padding:40px\"><div style=\"max-width:560px;margin:0 auto\"><h2 style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:20px\">Uma ultima coisa</h2><div style=\"background:#1a1a2e;border:1px solid #6366f1;border-radius:12px;padding:24px;margin:24px 0;text-align:center\"><div style=\"font-size:32px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:4px\">10% OFF no Pix</div><div style=\"font-size:14px;color:#aaa;margin-bottom:16px\">ou 5% OFF no cartao</div><div style=\"font-size:22px;color:#22c55e;font-weight:600\">R$177,30 no Pix</div></div><p style=\"color:#aaa\">Use o cupom <strong>ATENNA10</strong> no Pix ou <strong>ATENNA5</strong> no cartao. Valido por 48 horas.</p></div></body></html>",
        "options": {}
